Package: socketeer
Title: Interface to Linux-Style TCP Sockets
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: person("Martin", "Morgan",
    email = "martin.morgan@roswellpark.org",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package is a simple implementation of local
    (file-based) client and server sockets. Clients and servers
    support open() and close(). Server-side operations include
    send_to(), recv_from(), recv_any(); client-side operations are
    send(), recv().
License: Artistic-2.0
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
Imports: methods, BiocParallel
Suggests: testthat
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
